text: is a Japanese swimmer. She competed in the women's 200 metre individual medley at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. She also competed in the women's 50 metre freestyle and women's 100 metre freestyle events. In both events she did not advance to compete in the semi-finals. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Female freestyle swimmers
